{"article_id":"02SwFi0zpCNSkSlL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump has poured fresh scorn on US intelligence claims","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"of Russian hackers meddling in the US election .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"He tweeted :","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"`` Can you imagine","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"if the election results were the opposite","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and WE tried to play the Russia/CIA card .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"It would be called conspiracy theory ! ''","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The US president-elect also questioned","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"why the allegations were not widely made public before the election .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"His remarks set the incoming commander-in-chief against intelligence services","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that he will preside over .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"`` Unless you catch `` hackers '' in the act ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"it is very hard to determine who was doing the hacking .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Why was n't this brought up before election ? ''","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted on Monday morning .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"The FBI said in October","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"that it believed","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Russia was behind the Democratic Party hacks","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"but on Friday the CIA went further","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"by concluding","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Russia 's motive was to help Mr Trump .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"On Monday , the Hillary Clinton campaign ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"which lost to Mr Trump in last month 's election ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"it was supporting an effort by a handful of members of the electoral college","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to request an intelligence briefing on the latest hacking allegations .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Mrs Clinton 's top political adviser , John Podesta , told Politico :","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"`` The bipartisan electors ' letter","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"[ requesting the intelligence ]","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"raises very grave issues","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"involving our national security . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The electoral college meets next week","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"to ratify the results of the election .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Mr Trump 's latest Twitter tirade comes","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"a day after he told Fox News","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"the Democrats were disseminating the `` ridiculous '' hacking reports","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"because they lost the election ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and it was `` impossible to know '' who was behind it .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"On Friday , CIA officials told US media","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"they had `` high confidence ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that Russian hackers had attempted to sway the US election in Mr Trump 's favour .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"The Trump team responded to those reports in a statement :","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"`` These are the same people","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Saddam Hussein had weapons of mass destruction . ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Despite Donald Trump 's boasts to the contrary , he 's entering the White House with a very tenuous claims to a presidential mandate .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"He trails Democrat Hillary Clinton in the popular vote by 2.8 million votes ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"while he posted a comfortable Electoral College win ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"by historical standards it ranks towards the bottom of victory margins","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"( 46th out of 58 presidential contests ) .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"This likely explains why the Trump team has been pushing back so vociferously against the allegations","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that Russians hackers meddled in US politics","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"in an attempt","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to tilt the election to the Republican .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Like the Green Party-backed recounts in three key swing states , it could be viewed as undermining the legitimacy of Mr Trump 's victory .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Never mind that the recounts were extremely unlikely to appreciably change the election 's results","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"or that Russian hacking is well down the list of factors","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that contributed to Mrs Clinton 's defeat .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Mr Trump 's angry tweets , and the indignation","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"expressed by his supporters ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"is evidence enough","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that the president-elect feels threatened","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"- and is responding with sweeping denunciations of his critics .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"In the case of the Russian story , however , concern over foreign meddling is bipartisan ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"so Mr Trump 's recent diatribes may come at a high political price .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"On Sunday , John Bolton , the former US envoy to the UN","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"who is tipped to be named deputy secretary of state in the Trump administration ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"implied on Fox News","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that the Obama administration could have been behind the hacking .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Mr Bolton ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"who was one of the Bush administration 's most vocal advocates for the Iraq War ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"told the network :","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"`` It is not at all clear to me ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"just viewing this from the outside ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"that this hacking into the DNC and the RNC computers was not a false flag operation . ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"False flag is a term","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"commonly used by so-called conspiracy theorists ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"often to describe covert attacks by a government","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to advance its own agenda","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"by making it appear","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"as though someone else was responsible .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"`` If you think","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"the Russians did this ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"why did they leave fingerprints ? ''","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Mr Bolton added .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"President Barack Obama has ordered a complete review of the hacks ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"which targeted emails at the Democratic Party and the emails of a key aide to presidential nominee Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"The contents of the emails ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"passed to Wikileaks","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and posted online ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"were embarrassing to the Democrats","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"and shook up the presidential campaign .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Senior Republicans have joined Democrats","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"in calling for a full investigation .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"it `` defies belief '' that some Republicans are reluctant to review the alleged Russian tactics .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Republican Senator John McCain , chairman of the Senate Armed Services Committee , said in a joint statement on Sunday with top Democrats","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that the CIA 's report `` should alarm every American '' .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"While a company","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"that is breached by hackers","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"can really only work from the digital evidence","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"left behind ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"nation states or intelligence agencies have many more sources","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to draw on","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"when gathering evidence ,","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"said Rick Holland , vice president of strategy at cyber-security firm Digital Shadows .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"`` They have a full spectrum of capabilities such as signal intelligence and human intelligence , ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"adding :","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"`` It 's definitely not all cyber-based . ''","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"That extra evidence meant intelligence agencies could be more confident with their conclusions than many others ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"`` It 's certainly not simple , ''","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"said Mr Holland .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"`` But I do not think","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"attribution is impossible","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"when it comes to nation-states at all . ''","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Mr Holland admitted","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"that some nation states did sometimes run so-called `` false flag '' operations","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"that attempted to pin the blame for an attack on someone else .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"It could be difficult to unpick who was behind an attack","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"because both spies and cyber-criminals used each others ' attack tools and methods in a bid","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"to throw investigators off the scent .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"`` There is a lot down that rabbit hole","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"when it comes to nation states , ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"While nation states did try to hide their attacks ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"there were times","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"when knowing who was behind an attack was a useful diplomatic tool .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"`` Some nation states are very obvious","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and want you to know","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"who was behind it , ''","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"`` They will put you on notice","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"that they did this . ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":150,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":142,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":137,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":2,"right":140,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":139,"right":6,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":3,"right":138,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":143,"right":148,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":144,"right":147,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":167,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":155,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":152,"right":154,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":15,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":18,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","